Revision history for Mojolicious-Plugin-Gravatar

0.01  First version, released on an unsuspecting world.
0.02  Fixed a small html escaping bug (Akron).
0.03  Updated Mojolicious dependency to 3.97(fixed incompatibilities)
0.04  Added "scheme" options. Reformatted tests.
0.05  Use "secure.gravatar.com" when scheme is "https"

